 It assured him he wasn't doing all that in vain.

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
He had also started writing a book on mind magic, but that was still in its
 early stages, and nowhere near to completion.
 Publishing anything related to mind magic on a wide scale was going to be
 difficult, but he would find a way.

\end_layout

